	(text "J1 mates the Framework touchpad via a 51-conductor, \n0.30 mm-pitch FFC (Type A / same-side, ~0.20 mm thick). \n\nPinout is 1:1 with the touchpad (conn pin N = touchpad pin N);\nverify cable orientation by continuity before applying power.\n\nImportant note: the FFC must face pins upward on insertion into\ntouchpad, and face down for insertion into the bridge.\n\nExample Digikey FPC cable PN: Molex 0150150451"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 171.45 232.156 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "359c3719-64f4-4b21-b103-183c600f37e8")
	)
